events.name: Machine Learning Study Jam - Kick-off Meeting
events.description:
GDG Blantyre is our Machine Learning Study Jam - Kick-off Meeting that offers introductory session for material resources and support to those interested in Machines Learning to get started through Google's latest Machine Learning offering - ‘Machine Learning Crash Course (MLCC)’

EXAMPLE AGENDA:
9:00 AM Registration & Welcome Note
10:00 AM Introduction to Machine Learning Crash Course (MLCC)
11:00 AM Introduction to Tensorflow
11:40 AM Tensorflow Video Materials sharing
6:40 PM Closing Note & remarks
